#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.red_revolution_tomato_seeds
msgid ""
"During the flowering phase, skilled growers often employ natural pollination "
"methods, such as encouraging bees and other pollinators to transfer pollen "
"between flowers. This ensures genetic diversity and vitality in the "
"resulting seeds."
msgstr ""
"在植物开花阶段，熟练的种植者通常会采用自然授粉方法，例如鼓励蜜蜂和其他授粉者"
"在花朵之间传递花粉。这确保了种子的遗传多样性和生命力。"

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.pricing
